        <abstract>
            <para>This collection contains Invertebrate Vouchers derived from NEON Invertebrate Bycatch samples collect as part of the Carabid pitfall trapping protocol. Specimens are individually prepared (generally as pinned insects) and housed within the NEON Biorepository at the Arizona State University Biocollections.</para>
